This article needs to be updated . Please update this article to reflect recent events or newly available information. (July 2017)

This is a list of Spanish football transfers for the summer sale in 2017–18 season. Only moves from La Liga and Segunda División are listed.

The summer transfer window will begin on 1 July 2017, although a few transfers took place prior to that date. The window will close at midnight on 1 September 2017. Players without a club can join one at any time, either during or in between transfer windows. Clubs below La Liga level can also sign players on loan at any time. If needed, clubs can sign a goalkeeper on an emergency loan, if all others are unavailable.
